{
  "text": "Forty participants were selected after being prescreened using the WOMAC scores. [CITATION_1] The total WOMAC score on day zero (pretreatment) showed a mean (\u00b1 standard deviation [SD]) of 67.8 (\u00b18.8) for the group assigned to the placebo treatment and 62.5 (\u00b15.31) for the group assigned to the BRC treatment.",
